## - Primary entry: the gllvmTMB methods paper (Nakagawa et al., in prep).
##   Update the DOI / journal / volume / pages when the paper lands.
## - Recommended companions: cite TMB (Kristensen et al. 2016) for any
##   gllvmTMB fit, and sdmTMB (Anderson et al. 2025) when the spatial
##   path (`spatial_*()` keywords) is used.

